column51: Streamer was very nice and somehow actually enjoyed playing against a Legion.
Chill streamers. One survivor in the group was mildly unhappy with losing towards the end.
Poor performance on survivors' part but I also kinda sucked. They basically let me have a free win for some reason.
Somehow got a merciless 4k with memey Burger King(tm) Myers.
Good killer performance lead to early suicide. Farmed until 1 gen was left.
Bad survivors, map offering, and 4 medkits vs. Legion.
Really fun game with good players all around.
I got absolutely destroyed and complained a lot.
Had a lag switch cheater but 4k'd anyways.
